# Auto Job Scraper with Excel Export and Email Notifications

A Python automation tool that searches Indeed's job listings based on specific keywords and locations. It extracts
structured job data using firecrawl, exports results to Excel, and sends email notifications. 


## Features:
- Dynamically builds search URLs from user-provided keywords and locations
- Uses Pydantic schemas to guide the AI on how to format the extracted data
- Extracts structured job information (title, company, description, salary, location)
- Stores results in a formatted Excel workbook
- Sends automated email summaries of newly collected listings



## Built With:
- Language: Python
- Tools/Modules: Firecrawl, Pydantic, Openpyxl, SMTP, python-dotenv


