## How it runs:
- Hit run and enter the job keyword and location
- Open the job_listings.xlsx file to display the newly added job listing
- Find the email notification of the data

## Notes:
- Set an environment to store the FIRECRAWL_API_KEY, EMAIL_ADDRESS, and EMAIL_TEMP_PWD
- Your EMAIL_TEMP_PWD can be found by searching up google app passwords. Generate a temporary app password and name the device as 'server' (optionally)
- Install an extension to open the Excel file such as Excel Viewer on VS Code.


