## Challenges Faced:
- Traditional BeautifulSoup scraping was unreliable because Indeed content is dynamically rendered and highly secure.
- Investigated browser network requests using Chrome DevTools.
- Evaluated multiple scraping approaches before choosing Firecrawl for structured extraction.
- Expanded only one job description extraction by firecrawl using Pydantic models.
